---
title: Quick Chorizo & Cheesy Ciabatta Pizza Melt with Pear Salad
description: Our easy ciabatta and chorizo melt gives a traditional pizza some fierce competition. We’ve topped crispy ciabatta with a rich
tomato sugo and bursting corn kernels for extra flavour. Finished with gooey Cheddar cheese and ready in just 20 minutes, this
dinner won’t be hanging around for long.
